Create a simple app which shows weather information based on the city you enter. 
Example app design is shown in "example" dir. You can either use the defined design or create one of your own.

* App has to fetch weather information based on the input from the first screen.
* Keep the code clean.
* Write at least one unit test
* Write at least one UI test
* Use IoC container
* Use ReactiveX
* Use MVVM architecture with data binding.

---
* Weather API endpoint: http://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather?q={city name}&appid=7587eaff3affbf8e56a81da4d6c51d06
---